• Customers looking for reliable, everyday detailing services

SEO GOALS:
• Rank #1 for "car detailing [local area]" searches
• Dominate Google Map Pack for Niagara County
• Target service + location keywords (Lewiston, Clarence, Williamsville, East Amherst, Niagara Falls)
