CONTENT STRATEGY (Based on Diesel Dudes Analysis):

HOMEPAGE STRUCTURE:
• H1: Geographic authority ("Niagara County's Premier Luxury Car Detailing Service")
• Service areas preview with 8+ cities
• Emergency/mobile service emphasis
• Trust signals (licensed, insured, years experience)
• Multiple CTAs throughout

SERVICES PAGE STRUCTURE:
• 6-8 main services with 150-200 word descriptions
• Each service links to dedicated page
• Geographic mentions in each service description
• "Learn More" CTAs for each service

INDIVIDUAL SERVICE PAGES (1,200 words each):
1. Hero section (problem + solution + CTA)
2. "What's Included" (bulleted services)
3. Unique value proposition section
4. 5-step process explanation
5. "Common Issues We Solve" (6 specific problems)
6. Service coverage areas (Niagara County cities)
7. "Why Choose 716 Details" (3 key differentiators)
8. FAQ section (3+ questions)
9. Related services (internal linking)
10. Final CTA section

LOCATIONS STRATEGY:
• Main locations page listing all service areas
• Tier 1 cities (1,500 words): Clarence, Williamsville, East Amherst
• Tier 2 cities (500 words): Lewiston, Niagara Falls, Youngstown, North Tonawanda, Kenmore

LOCATION PAGE CONTENT:
• Local industry knowledge and challenges
• Neighborhood-specific coverage areas
• Local landmarks and business districts
• Climate/seasonal considerations
• Major local locations served
• Local expertise and relationships

SEO REQUIREMENTS:
• <title> (≤70 chars, service + main location + brand)
• <meta description> (155–160 chars, service + areas + CTA)
• H1 (one keyword-rich heading per page)
• LocalBusiness Schema (JSON-LD) with serviceType and areaServed
• Geographic keywords naturally integrated
• Internal linking between services and locations

